And as she reached the center of the vortex, Blight laughed and 
pressed a button causing the whirl pool to break apart, causing the 
ocean to close up above Alecto and the water began to fill the now 
unstable hole. This of course would not kill her, however from what I 
can gather it will greatly decrease her manueverability if she is 
encased in water.(Thats what im guessing anyways. Happened in G1 with 
hotrod underwater)
